description:
I want a simple TODO app. These are the features I want:
- Users should be able to signup and login. Account details: firstname, middlename, lastname, email, username, password.
- Multiple users with same email can exist. Username must be different.
- Email verification is a must. Users should not able to login to dashboard without verifying email. When the users click on the email link, users should visit a verification page on our app.
- Users should be able to create, read, update and delete tasks. A task simply a text(title of task).
- Users should be able to mark a task as completed or not completed.
- Users should be able view most recent tasks(paginated).
- Users should be able to search tasks using a search bar for title search and adjust pagination.
- Users should be able to logout.
- Users should be able to delete their account, update their name, email, and, password.

Authentication Flow.title: User Sign Up
events: User enters firstname, middlename, lastname, email, username, and password.
API checks if username is unique.
If username is unique, user is created in the database and an email-verification email is sent.
User clicks on the email verification link.
User is verified and can now login.

Authentication Flow.title: User Sign In
events: User enters username and password.
API checks if username and password are correct.
If correct and email is verified, user is logged in.

Authentication Flow.title: Email Verification
events: User clicks on the email verification link.
User visits a verification page on the app.

Authentication Flow.title: User Logout
events: User clicks logout button.
User is logged out.

Profile Management Flow.title: Update User Details
events: User navigates to /dashboard/settings.
User updates firstname, middlename, lastname, email, and/or password.
API updates user details through /api/v1/profile.

Profile Management Flow.title: Delete Account
events: User navigates to /dashboard/settings.
User initiates account deletion.
API deletes the user's account.

Task Management Flow.title: Create Task
events: User enters the task title.
API creates the task in the database.

Task Management Flow.title: Read Tasks (View Most Recent Tasks)
events: User navigates to dashboard.
API retrieves most recent tasks (paginated).

Task Management Flow.title: Update Task
events: User selects a task from the dashboard.
User updates the task title.
API updates the task in the database.

Task Management Flow.title: Delete Task
events: User selects a task from the dashboard.
User deletes the task.
API deletes the task from the database.

Task Management Flow.title: Mark Task as Completed/Not Completed
events: User selects a task from the dashboard.
User toggles the task status between completed and not completed.
API updates the task status in the database.

Task Management Flow.title: Search Tasks
events: User enters task title in the search bar.
User adjusts pagination if necessary.
API retrieves matching tasks.

- Settings: Manage Account Settings including Delete Account.
